    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but my doctor didn't even emphasize the \"resistance\" thing, they just said take them for 10 days. i'm just really worried about the side effects for the next week if i keep going. if i can see with my own eyes that the infection is 100% gone, isn't it basically just unnecessary medicine at this point? it feels like it's doing more harm than good now.",
